title: El Celler de Triton
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Beer/Wine, Spanish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu features mostly vegetarian food. Saladas, tapas, snack foods, sandwiches and wraps, tofu and seitan, veggie croquettes, organic wine available, desserts. Dark, cozy interior. A daily menu (veg burger, salad, fries), combination plate (main, side, salad) and a la carte items can be found for both lunch and dinner.
